title: I Tricked Food Critics Into Eating Cockroach
description: In this video, Max Fosh tricks food critics into unknowingly eating a cockroach as part of a social experiment.
summary: Max Fosh pulls a prank on food critics by sneaking a cockroach into their food and observing their reactions.
payoff: The payoff comes when the food critics realize they have eaten a cockroach, leading to hilarious and shocked reactions.
